item.title: Abdul Samad Shishir | UI/UX Designer
item.description: Hello! I am Abdul Samad Shishir, a 29 year old UI/UX Designer, living in Dhaka, Bangladesh. I have an eye for detail and a passion for what I do. Currently working with awesome guys at Orbitax. It is a personal website of a designer who passionate about design. People call Abdul Samad shsihir as a Bootstrap Guru. Have lot of experience in mockup conversion into Bootstrap or Foundation.
